      • cleanup

        public void cleanup()
             throws IOException
        To clean up the test environment over underfs cluster system, so that we can re-use the running system for the next test round instead of turning on/off it from time to time. This function is expected to be called either before or after each test case which avoids certain overhead from the bootstrap.
        Throws:
        IOException - when the operation fails
